sequenceDiagram
    participant User
    participant API
    participant UserService
    participant UserModel
    participant Database

    User->>API: POST /users/register (Valid Data)
    API->>UserService: register_user(user_data)
    UserService->>UserModel: validate(user_data)
    UserModel-->>UserService: valid
    UserService->>Database: check if email exists
    Database-->>UserService: email not found
    UserService->>Database: INSERT INTO users
    Database-->>UserService: insert success
    UserService-->>API: return success response
    API-->>User: 201 Created ("User Registered Successfully")
